# Frontend Configuration

# Recommended:
# - For production domain deployments behind reverse proxy, set these to your public domain:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://your-domain.com/api
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_MEDIA_BASE_URL=https://your-domain.com/media
# - If omitted, app will try safe runtime fallbacks.

# For Server-Side Rendering (Optional)
# If your backend is running in a different container or internal network
# INTERNAL_API_URL=http://backend:8000

# Local development examples:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000/api
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MEDIA_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000/media
